219
0:12:40.12,000 --> 0:12:43,000
their brains predict a hammering heartbeat,

220
0:12:43.469,000 --> 0:12:44,000
sweaty hands,

221
0:12:44.912,000 --> 0:12:49,000
so much so that they are unable to actually take the test.

222
0:12:50.436,000 --> 0:12:51,000
