227
0:13:08.031,000 --> 0:13:09,000
and ace that test ...

228
0:13:10.449,000 --> 0:13:12,000
or, you know, give a talk

229
0:13:12.648,000 --> 0:13:15,000
in front of hundreds of people on a stage where you're being filmed.

230
0:13:16.268,000 --> 0:13:17,000
(Laughter)

231
0:13:17.887,000 --> 0:13:18,000
I'm serious.

232
0:13:19.158,000 --> 0:13:2,000
(Laughter)

233
0:13:21.529,000 --> 0:13:25,000
And research shows that when students learn

234
0:13:26.014,000 --> 0:13:28,000
to make this kind of energized determination

235
0:13:28.769,000 --> 0:13:29,000
instead of anxiety,

236
0:13:30.234,000 --> 0:13:32,000
they perform better on tests.

237
0:13:33.145,000 --> 0:13:37,000
And that determination seeds their brain to predict differently in the future

238
0:13:38.063,000 --> 0:13:41,000
so that they can get their butterflies flying in formation.

239
0:13:41.507,000 --> 0:13:43,000
And if they do that often enough,

240
0:13:43.683,000 --> 0:13:45,000
they not only can pass a test

241
0:13:46.255,000 --> 0:13:49,000
but it will be easier for them to pass their courses,

242
0:13:49.303,000 --> 0:13:51,000
and they might even finish college,

243
0:13:52.288,000 --> 0:13:56,000
which has a huge impact on their future earning potential.

244
0:13:57.458,000 --> 0:14:,000
So I call this emotional intelligence in action.

245
0:14:01.93,000 --> 0:14:04,000
Now you can cultivate this emotional intelligence yourself

